name: Hillary Rodham Clinton
abstract: Hillary Diane Rodham Clinton is an American politician who was the 67th United States Secretary of State from 2009 to 2013, serving under President Barack Obama. She was previously a United States Senator for New York from 2001 to 2009.
related_searches: Bill Clinton is Hillary Rodham Clinton's spouse.
